<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1292">everquest.allakhazam.com/...quest=1292</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
This quest starts in Western Wastes and is given out by Markil Rargon. When Markil is hailed he will talk about the fusibility of elements and ask you to bring him 4 items to combine in a box he gives you. After you combine the 4 items and hand the combined box back to him he will give you the Strength <br>
of the Elements. The 4 items that are needed are: <br>
<br>
-- Fusible Coral Ore - Off Phinigel Autropos in Kedge Keep <br>
-- Fusible Earthen Ore - From Master Yael in the Hole <br>
-- Fusible Igneous Ore - Ground spawn by the large volcano in Sky Fire mountains around 900, -1500 <br>
-- Fusible Velium Ore - Off a large air elemental named Guardian Kozzalym in <br>
Western Wastes.<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Markil is a Human NPC.  I think he paths North-South near the East Wall in Western Wastes <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uarantrunemaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arant Runemaster</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://verbalsabre.50megs.com/images/cooked.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/5/02 5:25:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4563.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question</span><hr size=1> Kozzalym is a 5 day spawn, unless they changed it since I camped him. /em pats his Strength of the Elements. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=4563.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=4563.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4563.topic&index=17><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=4563.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=4563.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4563.topic>